  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2>Solo Walking Holidays in Europe</h2>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13094668/microsoftteams-image-4.png?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="solo walking holiday" data-udi="umb://media/12f21180005949fa8870ec769524049d" /></p>
<div>
<p>Solo travelers, the great outdoors is calling. Set the pace, choose the path, and make it yours - No set itineraries, just endless possibilities waiting to be discovered.</p>
<p>With supplement-free options and single rooms, you’ll enjoy your holiday just like everyone else.</p>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Why book a solo holiday with Inghams?</h2>
</div>
<p> </p>
<!-- Row container with flex layout and wrap -->
<div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 20px; justify-content: center; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;"><!-- Card 1 -->
<div style="flex: 1 1 30%; max-width: 20%; min-width: 230px; margin: 10px; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
<h3 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.2em;">In resort reps</h3>
<p>Relax and travel solo without feeling alone. Our Inghams reps are friendly and experienced, so they'll make sure you have everything you need for the ultimate solo holiday.</p>
</div>
<!-- Card 2 -->
<div style="flex: 1 1 30%; max-width: 20%; min-width: 230px; margin: 10px; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
<h3 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.2em;">Travel solo, your way</h3>
<p>Our solo walking holidays provide the ideal mix of solitude and exploration, whether you seek an action-packed getaway or a tranquil lakeside retreat.</p>
</div>
<!-- Card 3 -->
<div style="flex: 1 1 30%; max-width: 20%; min-width: 230px; margin: 10px; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
<h3 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.2em;">No single supplements</h3>
<p>Many of our hotels offer a supplement-free option for travelling solo, or single rooms where you'll be able to enjoy your holiday just like everyone else.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">How to book your holiday</h3>
<p style="text-align: center;">Simply give us a call to book your holiday. Flights, hotel and transport? We’ve got you covered.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call us to book today</a></p>
</div>
<h2>Discover our hotels for single travellers</h2>
<p>Get away from it all, and have a holiday to remember. With single travellers in mind, we’ve selected some of the best hotels for people who like to travel alone. From Italy with its stunning lakeside views, to Austria and its majestic mountains, our single-friendly hotels are designed to make you feel at home, with plenty of things to do and see whilst you’re there. </p>
<div>
<h3 style="text-align: left;">Solo holidays in Austria</h3>
</div>
<div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/0e3acebd773c41129a5137bcda17e19c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0e3acebd773c41129a5137bcda17e19c}" title="Alpenhotel Kramerwirt">Alpenhotel Kramerwirt, Mayrhofen</a></strong></p>
<p><img style="width: 314px; height: 193px;" src="/media/13095413/kramerwirt_panorama_whirlpool-1.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="Alpenhotel Kramerwirt" data-udi="umb://media/8846a246b91f4c86b3084e1b0656f2e5" /></p>
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []">This family run hotel offers exceptional hospitality, comfort and home-style cooking in an Austrian mountain setting. </p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/9ed9d1dc5645419e85115978c169b654" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9ed9d1dc5645419e85115978c169b654}" title="Bergresort Seefeld">Bergresort, Seefeld</a></strong></p>
<p><img style="width: 314px; height: 193px;" src="/media/13095415/sommer-aussenansicht-1-1.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="bergresort, seefeld" data-udi="umb://media/d47d263354f84ce68427a3f167ea5376" /></p>
<p>This hotel in Seefeld features a lovely spa and landscaped gardens, and boasts a distinctive rustic ambiance in its interior design. </p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9}" title="Hotel Mon Repos"></a></div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/d0764a97320749fe824365958421503b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d0764a97320749fe824365958421503b}" title="Hotel Saalbacher Hof (Saalbach)">Hotel Saalbacherhof, Saalbach</a></strong></p>
<p><img style="width: 314px; height: 193px;" src="/media/13107090/2023-september-garten-saalbacherhof-markus-landauer-12.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/84a2bcff0bef4db8a019f874d311bdb3" /></p>
<p>This hotel is located just 50 metres from the Schattberg and Bernkogel gondolas, so you're perfectly situated to explore all that the resort has to offer. </p>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h3>Solo holidays in France</h3>
<div class="g4">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/ee980d982293408db473e647a1892aac" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ee980d982293408db473e647a1892aac}" title="Hotel Champs Fleuris"><strong>Hotel Champs Fleuris, Morzine</strong></a></p>
<p><img style="width: 314px; height: 193px;" src="/media/13095425/champs-fleuris-28.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="Hotel Champs Fleuris" data-udi="umb://media/e08d865f19e84862a6b05b704d76e6ce" /></p>
<p>Experience the ultimate in comfort and luxury at this beautiful hotel, which is known for its delectable cuisine, comfortable rooms, and stunning views of the mountains.</p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/29edcd3c50e4458281799c0617b52ba5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/29edcd3c50e4458281799c0617b52ba5}" title="Hotel La Folie Douce"><strong>Hotel La Folie Douce, Chamonix</strong></a></p>
<p><img style="width: 314px; height: 193px;" src="/media/13095426/folie-douce-18-1.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="Hotel La Folie Douce" data-udi="umb://media/662eec80991a4db6b5259202fa7d066b" /></p>
<p><span>Experience the best views of Chamonix from this hotel, which also features a large spa with a sauna, relaxation room, sun terrace, and steam room.</span></p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9}" title="Hotel Mon Repos"></a></div>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3>Solo holidays in Switzerland and Slovenia</h3>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/8fa1210d0a794f8597980dec5856b80f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8fa1210d0a794f8597980dec5856b80f}" title="Hotel Alex">Hotel Alex, Zermatt</a></strong></p>
<p><img style="width: 314px; height: 193px;" src="/media/13107091/hotel_alex_zermatt_classic_double_room-1.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/6a441db830ce48529986fe0fc0ba5971" /></p>
<p>Hotel Alex is a charming hotel offering comfortable and sophisticated rooms, conveniently situated just 2 minutes walk from The Matterhorn Mountain. The hotel offers a large indoor pool, jacuzzi and sauna.</p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/b27591e078194ddd981ff8e811b26cba" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b27591e078194ddd981ff8e811b26cba}" title="Hotel Kompas">Hotel Kompas, Kranjska Gora</a></strong></p>
<p> </p>
<p><img style="width: 258px; height: 193px;" src="/media/13107092/140971.jpg?width=258&amp;height=193" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/1e4dde30e2e541f7994bd20bd8f974ba" /></p>
<p>This hotel is located amidst lush meadows and is a short distance from the town centre. You can relax and rejuvenate in the luxurious spa, featuring saunas, a Turkish steam room, an indoor pool, and a whirlpool.</p>
</div>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3 style="text-align: left;">Solo holidays in Italy</h3>
<div class="g4">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/919b13aa1fae4bc68aa9503210e88b44" href="/{localLink:umb://document/919b13aa1fae4bc68aa9503210e88b44}" title="Hotel Adria"><strong>Hotel Adria, Merano</strong></a></p>
<p><img style="width: 314px; height: 193px;" src="/media/13095420/adria-hotel-merano.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="Hotel Adria" data-udi="umb://media/a53674240667434d9b7b9d280b4e36c8" /></p>
<p>This beautiful, Art Nouveau gem is located in Merano's Obermais neighbourhood. It boasts a free wellness centre with an indoor pool, a restaurant, and a complimentary gym.</p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/da18898c2b41431b907c91a66c4f4fc3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/da18898c2b41431b907c91a66c4f4fc3}" title="Hotel Rodella"><strong>Hotel Rodella, Selva</strong></a></p>
<p><img style="width: 314px; height: 193px;" src="/media/13095421/hotel-rodella-selva-21-1.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="Hotel Rodella" data-udi="umb://media/f1bbc73e46bb4a139c27dfa4ebfbfa20" /></p>
<p>You’ll love the hotel’s Natura classification, which means it uses 100% green energy. It also has great facilities and offers a free daily packed lunch.</p>
</div>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/b2b4e84a791b41488510bc4662951771" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b2b4e84a791b41488510bc4662951771}" title="Hotel Antonella"><strong>Hotel Antonella, Malcesine</strong></a></p>
<div class="g4">
<p><img src="/media/13108662/hotel_antonella_malcesine-1.png" alt="hotel antonella" data-udi="umb://media/f7f9644444104ec2a1bb66627e1884db" /></p>
<p>A cosy, family-run spot by the Zamboni family, offers warm hospitality and a convenient location near Lake Garda, with easy access to Malcesine, a scenic lakeside path, and the Monte Baldo cable car for excellent walking trails.</p>
</div>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">How to book your holiday</h3>
<p style="text-align: center;">Simply give us a call to book your holiday. Flights, hotel and transport? We’ve got you covered.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call us to book today</a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/cfba37b7bc6a47319fa4541d4470c776" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cfba37b7bc6a47319fa4541d4470c776}" title="Solo" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">View all Deals</a></p>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Travel With Confidence</h2>
<p style="text-align: left;">When you book with us you can travel with confidence. <a data-udi="umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae}" title="In Safe Hands">We’ve put extra measures in place </a>for your peace of mind. We’ll help keep both you and your money safe.</p>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13095389/inghams-in-safe-hands-charcoal.png?width=500&amp;height=126.45687645687646" alt="in safe hands" data-udi="umb://media/afba17a916e84fcc848acce5dda4f9c4" /></p>]]></bodyText>
